{"tid":440254,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"治癒系女神IU又換髮型了 美到連粉絲都大喊「感謝」","createTime":"2017-10-18T14:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T11:24:12.000Z","uid":34643,"like":111,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"8fabe95e4489c7fcc689e29fe22caad269c7863e","tid":440254,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.insight.co.kr/static/2017/09/13/700/2d78muig2duy04v3f2rp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2017%2F09%2F13%2F700%2F2d78muig2duy04v3f2rp.jpg&h=f54e4fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不久前SOLO時期IU還是一頭清爽俏皮的金色長Lob捲髮，沒想到多日不見的她又換了新造型。<br />\n<br />\n照片中的IU髮色從金色變為了純黑色短髮，迷人的大波浪卷讓整個人看起來多了層次感。 空氣劉海露出飽滿的額頭，明媚動人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile9.uf.tistory.com/original/9976183359E75AF302AE04\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile9.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F9976183359E75AF302AE04&h=25a40958&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile5.uf.tistory.com/original/9920383359E75AEF09C328\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile5.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F9920383359E75AEF09C328&h=ffff7f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cfile22.uf.tistory.com/original/99709A3359E75AF1316AC1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile22.uf.tistory.com%2Foriginal%2F99709A3359E75AF1316AC1&h=827dd248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU白皮膚在黑髮的映襯下更顯白皙透亮，而粉絲們也貌似更愛IU的黑髮造型，紛紛留言表示「謝謝你的黑髮」、「我愛短髮IU」、「真女神」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DL17VxjV4AAwuTs.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDL17VxjV4AAwuTs.jpg%3Aorig&h=8a36575e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3897a51f9e4a259b226fd75db25ae7dcaef38ca","tid":440254,"uid":34643,"like":62,"dislike":4,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:59:07.000Z","msg":"呢種及肩短髮都係超正<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DKigBvEVwAEy5Re.j